s a lot&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-internal-linking-plugins-for-wordpress/\">5 Best Internal Linking Plugins for WordPress</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20729:\"<p>Looking for the best internal linking plugins to help improve your SEO?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Internal links play an important role in search engine optimization (SEO). However, adding them manually can be very time-consuming and laborious, especially if your website has a lot of pages.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you some of the best internal linking plugins for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-importance-of-internal-links-in-seo\">The Importance of Internal Links in SEO</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-best-internal-linking-plugins-for-wordpress-our-expert-picks\">5 Best Internal Linking Plugins for WordPress: Our Expert Picks</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-link-whisper\">2. Link Whisper</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-internal-link-juicer\">3. Internal Link Juicer</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-rank-math\">4. Rank Math</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-yoast-seo\">5. Yoast SEO</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-internal-linking-plugin-for-wordpress-your-faqs-answered\">The Best Internal Linking Plugin for WordPress: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-an-internal-linking-plugin\">What is an internal linking plugin?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-is-internal-linking-important-for-seo\">Why is internal linking important for SEO?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-the-best-internal-linking-plugin-for-wordpress\">What is the best internal linking plugin for WordPress?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-internal-linking-plugin-for-wordpress-our-top-pick\">The Best Internal Linking Plugin for WordPress: Our Top Pick</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-importance-of-internal-links-in-seo\">The Importance of Internal Links in SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Internal links are links between <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/posts-vs-pages-in-wordpress/\" title=\"Posts vs. Pages in WordPress — Everything You Need to Know\">pages or posts</a> on your site, and they play a huge role in on-page SEO because, among other things they:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Pass PageRank (SEO value)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Give search engines topical context of a page</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Contribute to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-permalink-structure/\" title=\"What’s the Best WordPress Permalink Structure for SEO?\">site architecture</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Give users a better experience</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Help increase time on page</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-crawling-and-indexing/\" title=\"What is Crawling and Indexing in SEO? [Beginners Guide]\">Improves crawlability</a> and results in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/indexing-in-seo/\" title=\"What is Crawling and Indexing in SEO? [Beginners Guide]\">better indexing</a>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Internal links are more important than they’re usually given credit for. But they’re a powerful way to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/wordpress-seo-tips/\" title=\"21+ WordPress SEO Tips for Beginners [Ultimate Cheat List]\">boost your SEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While WordPress provides an easy way to add links to your blog <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/posts-vs-pages-in-wordpress/\" title=\"Posts vs. Pages in WordPress — Everything You Need to Know\">posts and pages</a>, it’s a manual method. This means it is time-consuming and can increase the chances of you missing an opportunity to link to an important page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And that’s why having an internal linking plugin comes in handy. It helps ensure you can strategically <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-link-assistant-can-save-you-time-on-internal-and-external-link-building/\" title=\"6 Ways Link Assistant Can Save You Time On Internal Link Building\">add links between your posts and pages</a>, even at scale.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-5-best-internal-linking-plugins-for-wordpress-our-expert-picks\">5 Best Internal Linking Plugins for WordPress: Our Expert Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve curated a list of expertly picked <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-a-plugin-beginners-guide-to-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"What is a Plugin? The Beginner’s Guide to WordPress Plugins\">WordPress plugins</a> to help make internal linking easy. This will result in boosting your on-page SEO and drive more traffic to your site. Let’s dive right into it, shall we?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is a powerful tool that makes it easy to add internal links in WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-96547\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">AIOSEO</a> is a powerful yet easy-to-use SEO plugin that has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of smart business owners use AIOSEO to help them boost their search engine rankings and drive qualified site traffic.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One feature that makes this possible is Link Assistant.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Link Assistant is an AI-powered tool that crawls your website and provides a detailed report of the links on your WordPress website and the number of internal links, outbound links, and affiliate links on your site. It also shows you the number of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-easily-find-and-fix-orphan-pages-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Find and Fix Orphan Pages in WordPress\">orphaned pages</a> you have so you can create links to and from them.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"329\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Divi-seo-link-assistant.png\" alt=\"Link Assistant is a handy feature that helps build internal links and boost your SEO.\" class=\"wp-image-87481\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Divi-seo-link-assistant.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Divi-seo-link-assistant-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Divi-seo-link-assistant-600x282.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>However, Link Assistant does more than audit the links on your site. It also shows you internal linking opportunities under the <strong>Links Report</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"381\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report.png\" alt=\"To help boost your internal linking strategy, Link Assistant\" class=\"wp-image-79017\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report-300x163.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report-600x327.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you click on the <strong>Linking Opportunities </strong>tab, the report shows you all the outbound internal and inbound internal links you can add to your posts. It also shows you the exact phrase and the anchor text on which Link Assistant will create the link.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"354\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-1024x354.png\" alt=\"You can edit the anchor text in Link Assistant.\" class=\"wp-image-79022\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-1024x354.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-300x104.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-768x266.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-600x208.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1.png 1078w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If everything looks good, all it takes to add the link is to click the <strong>Add Link</strong> button. If you need to edit the anchor text or move the link to a better phrase, simply click the pencil icon, and you can edit the anchor text. You don’t even need to open the blog post in editor mode.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Link Assistant makes internal linking a breeze. Plus, it gives you complete control of your internal link building, making it the most powerful internal linking plugin for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-link-assistant-to-optimize-your-internal-linking-strategy/\" title=\"How to Use Link Assistant to Optimize Your Internal Linking Strategy\">guide on using Link Assistant</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $49.60. Free version available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-link-whisper\">2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/linkwhisper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Link Whisper\">Link Whisper</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper.png\" alt=\"Link Whisper home page\" class=\"wp-image-167488\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper-300x120.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper-600x240.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper-150x60.png 150w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-link-whisper-225x90.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/linkwhisper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Link Whisper\">Link Whisper</a> is a premium WordPress plugin designed to help automate internal link building on your site. The plugin is easy to use and works right inside the WordPress editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Link Whisper suggests relevant internal links as you type your content. It can also help you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-easily-find-and-fix-orphan-pages-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Find and Fix Orphan Pages in WordPress\">find orphan pages and posts</a> and then suggests links to add to them. The plugin also gives detailed reports of all the links on your site, including all internal and external links plus broken links.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Link Whisper, you can build strategic internal links quickly, helping to boost your content to the top of the SERPs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $77 for a single site license.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-3-internal-link-juicer\">3. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/internal-links/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Internal Link Juicer\">Internal Link Juicer</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/internal-links/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"314\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-internal-plugins-interal-juicer.png\" alt=\"Internal Link Juicer home page\" class=\"wp-image-254700\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-internal-plugins-interal-juicer.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-internal-plugins-interal-juicer-300x134.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-internal-plugins-interal-juicer-600x268.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/internal-links/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Internal Link Juicer\">Internal Link Juicer</a> is another WordPress internal linking plugin to have on your radar. It’s a free plugin making it a great alternative if you’re on a shoestring budget. However, despite being free, it’s still an excellent tool for automatically building internal links in your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can add specific keywords and phrases in the plugin, and it will automatically add links for you. This has the advantage of giving you more control over your internal links. For example, it helps you diversify your anchor text, ensuring all links are natural and don’t appear computer-generated.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Internal Link Juicer also lets you blacklist and whitelist specific posts from internal linking. It also allows you to limit the number of links per post.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-4-rank-math\">4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Rank Math\">Rank Math</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"284\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath.png\" alt=\"Rank Math home page\" class=\"wp-image-143352\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath-300x122.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/best-serp-preview-tools-rankmath-600x243.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\">Rank Math</a> is another WordPress SEO plugin that comes with basic features that help boost your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-internal-links-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Add Internal Links In WordPress: The Easy Way\">internal link building strategy</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like AIOSEO, the plugin scans your website for links and looks for internal linking opportunities. Unlike AIOSEO, however, Rank Math&#8217;s link builder isn’t automatic, it’s manual. Linking suggestions are shown in your WordPress content editor, then you have to manually copy the suggested link and insert it into your text.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $59/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-5-yoast-seo\">5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Yoast SEO\">Yoast SEO</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"466\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/best-serp-preview-tools-yoast.png\" alt=\"Yoast home page\" class=\"wp-image-143353\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/best-serp-preview-tools-yoast.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/best-serp-preview-tools-yoast-300x200.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/best-serp-preview-tools-yoast-600x399.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Yoast SEO\">Yoast SEO</a> is another popular WordPress SEO plugin designed to help users optimize their sites to rank high in search results. The plugin also features a basic internal linking tool for premium users. The tool scans your content for internal links and checks for linking opportunities.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yoast, like Rank Math, does not automate internal link building. Instead, it offers linking suggestions, and then you copy the suggested link and embed it in your post.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not sure which WordPress plugin to choose between AIOSEO, Yoast, and Rank Math?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s a detailed comparison of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/yoast-vs-rank-math-vs-all-in-one-seo/\" title=\"Yoast vs Rank Math vs All in One SEO: Which Is Better?\">Yoast vs. Rank Math vs. AIOSEO</a> to help you see which is the clear winner.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $99/year for the core plugin. Addons are purchased separately.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-best-internal-linking-plugin-for-wordpress-your-faqs-answered\">The Best Internal Linking Plugin for WordPress: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-an-internal-linking-plugin\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What is an internal linking plugin?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>An internal linking plugin is designed to help website owners and developers manage and optimize internal links within their websites. It facilitates connecting different pages or posts within the same site to enhance navigation and SEO.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-why-is-internal-linking-important-for-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\"><strong>Why is internal linking important for SEO?</strong></h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Internal linking is crucial for SEO as it helps search engines understand the structure and hierarchy of your website. It also distributes page authority and helps users navigate through your content, improving user experience.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-the-best-internal-linking-plugin-for-wordpress\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What is the best internal linking plugin for WordPress?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>All In One SEO (AIOSEO) is the best internal linking plugin for WordPress. It uses AI to parse your site and identify linking opportunities. Plus, you can add internal links automatically without opening the pages in editing mode.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-best-internal-linking-plugin-for-wordpress-our-top-pick\">The Best Internal Linking Plugin for WordPress: Our Top Pick&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our top pick for the best internal linking plugin for WordPress is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">AIOSEO</a>. The plugin has a powerful AI-powered algorithm that discovers linking opportunities and suggests the perfect placement. And because link insertion is automatic, scaling your internal linking is a breeze.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides internal link building, AIOSEO has a comprehensive feature set to help you with most facets of SEO. With AIOSEO, you reduce the plugin count on your site while powering it for success.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you find the best internal linking plugin for WordPress. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\" title=\"The Ultimate Link Building Guide You Need for 2023\">ultimate link building guide</a> or our tutorial on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-start-a-small-business-blog/\">starting a small business blog</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-internal-linking-plugins-for-wordpress/\">5 Best Internal Linking Plugins for WordPress</a> first appeared on <a h