ools to help boost your clickthrough rate.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-a-meta-description-tool\">What is a Meta Description Tool?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-best-meta-description-tools-to-boost-your-clickthrough-rate-our-top-picks\">7 Best Meta Description Tools to Boost Your Clickthrough Rate: Our Top Picks</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-frase\">2. Frase</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-copy-ai\">3. Copy.ai</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-jasper\">4. Jasper</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-copysmith\">5. Copysmith</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-rytr\">6. Rytr</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-writesonic\">7. Writesonic</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-meta-description-tools-your-faqs-answered\">Meta Description Tools: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-a-meta-description\">What is a meta description?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-meta-description-tools\">What are meta description tools?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-can-meta-description-tools-help-with-seo\">Can meta description tools help with SEO?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-meta-description-tools-to-boost-your-clickthrough-rate-our-top-pick\">The Best Meta Description Tools to Boost Your Clickthrough Rate: Our Top Pick</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-a-meta-description-tool\">What is a Meta Description Tool?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A meta description tool is software that helps you generate meta descriptions automatically within no time. The meta descriptions are also SEO-friendly since they are generated from your keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Meta descriptions are essential to SEO as they serve as your sales pitch on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs). The more compelling your meta descriptions are, the higher the chances are that searchers will click on your search listing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And this is why you should use the best meta description generator for your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-best-meta-description-tools-to-boost-your-clickthrough-rate-our-top-picks\">7 Best Meta Description Tools to Boost Your Clickthrough Rate: Our Top Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2023\">supercharge your SEO</a> with compelling meta descriptions?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s our expertly curated list of the best meta description tools to help you do that.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO has one of the best meta description tools built in.\" class=\"wp-image-96547\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">AIOSEO</a> is the best WordPress SEO plugin on the market and has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of savvy website owners and marketers trust the plugin to help them dominate SERPs and drive relevant traffic to their sites. This is because the plugin has many powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">SEO features and modules</a> to help you optimize your website for search engines and users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most loved features is the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/dominate-search-rankings-with-aioseos-ai-title-description-generator/\" title=\"[NEW] Dominate Search Rankings with AIOSEO’s AI Title/Description Generator\">AI Title/Description Generator</a>. This powerful tool built on the ChatGPT platform automatically generates SEO titles and meta descriptions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Crafting SEO-friendly meta descriptions with the AI Title/Description Generator is super easy. All you have to do is scroll down to the AIOSEO General Settings section at the bottom of your article. Here, you’ll find the AIOSEO meta box, where you’ll find a robot button inside the <strong>Meta Description</strong> box.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"267\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-meta-description-tools-robot-icon.png\" alt=\"Robot icon in meta description field.\" class=\"wp-image-254162\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-meta-description-tools-robot-icon.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-meta-description-tools-robot-icon-300x114.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-meta-description-tools-robot-icon-600x228.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When you click on the Robot icon, AIOSEO will generate 5 meta description suggestions based on your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"462\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples.png\" alt=\"Meta description examples.\" class=\"wp-image-170248