commends/frase-io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Frase\">Frase</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/frase-io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"324\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase.png\" alt=\"Frase home page\" class=\"wp-image-170958\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase-300x139.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase-600x278.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase-130x60.png 130w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/best-ai-seo-tools-frase-194x90.png 194w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/frase-io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Frase\">Frase</a> is a powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress/\" title=\"The 9 Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress in 2023\">AI SEO tool</a> designed to make content creation easy. While it’s mostly known for automatically generating SEO-friendly content briefs, it also has many other features that are useful to SEOs. One of them is their meta description tool.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Frase utilizes natural language processing to analyze your content and generate relevant meta descriptions. Its intuitive interface and the ability to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-content-optimization-tools-for-seo/\" title=\"7 Best Content Optimization Tools for SEO\">optimize content for SEO </a>make it a popular choice for many users.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To generate meta descriptions, you need to input your SEO title and primary keyword. The meta description tool will then give you 3 suggestions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Frase is one of the best