</strong>: The meta description generator is free. Paid plans start at $36/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-4-jasper\">4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/jasper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Jasper\">Jasper</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/jasper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/image3best-meta-description-generator-jasper.png\" alt=\"Jasper home page\" class=\"wp-image-254172\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/image3best-meta-description-generator-jasper.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/image3best-meta-description-generator-jasper-300x147.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/image3best-meta-description-generator-jasper-600x295.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/jasper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Jasper\">Jasper</a> is an AI writing assistant that’s probably been around longer than most. The tool is well-known for generating any kind of article, from long-form blog posts to social media posts and everything in between.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jasper also has a handy meta description tool that’s easy to use. To generate a meta description, simply enter the company/product name, blog post title, blog post description and target keyword. Click generate, and the tool will generate multiple suggestions depending on how many you set it to generate. You can further fine-tune the generated meta description to suit your needs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because Jasper’s suite of AI tools is designed to improve the content workflow, it doesn’t come cheap. However, it’s definitely worth the investment if you’re producing a lot of content and have the budget for the tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $40/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-5-copysmith\">5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/copysmith/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Copysmith\">Copysmith</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/copysmith/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"328\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-copysmith.png\" alt=\"Copysmith homepage.\" class=\"wp-image-254173\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-copysmith.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-copysmith-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-copysmith-600x281.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/copysmith/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Copysmith\">Copysmith</a> is an AI writing tool designed specifically for eCommerce sites. It automates many content writing functions, such as product descriptions, social media, captions, and article rewriting. The tool also comes with a meta description generator that you can use. However, you must first create a Copysmith account.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Copysmith’s meta description tool generates meta descriptions from your keywords, company name, and other information you input. The tool also analyzes your content to understand its context to generate meta descriptions that are engaging, concise, and optimized for search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A meta description tool like Copysmith makes generating <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\" title=\"How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO (Boost CTR &amp; Rankings)\">SEO-friendly meta descriptions</a> a breeze.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $19/month.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-6-rytr\">6. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rytr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Rytr\">Rytr</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"337\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-rytr.png\" alt=\"Rytr home page\" class=\"wp-image-254179\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-rytr.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-rytr-300x144.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-rytr-600x289.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rytr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Rytr\">Rytr</a> is a content writing and optimization tool that’s fast becoming popular. The tool automatically generates blog post outlines, calls to action (CTAs) for ads and landing pages, meta descriptions, and more.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll have to sign up for a Rytr account to use all the tool&#8217;s features, including the meta description generator, even though it’s free.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best parts of this meta description tool is that it can create meta descriptions in 30 languages and counting. This makes it one of the best meta description tools for <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/the-beginners-guide-to-wordpress-multilingual-seo/\" title=\"The Beginner’s Guide to WordPress Multilingual SEO\">multilingual websites</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While Rytr’s functionality is limited when compared to other tools on this list, it’s one of the best options for bloggers or small businesses on a shoestring budget.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $9/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-writesonic\">7. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/writesonic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Writesonic\">Writesonic</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"363\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-writesonic.png\" alt=\"Writesonic home page\" class=\"wp-image-254198\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-writesonic.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-writesonic-300x156.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/best-ai-seo-tools-writesonic-600x311.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/writesonic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Writesonic\">Writesonic</a> is an AI writing software that runs on OpenAI’s GPT technology. The tool is a suite of 60+ content creation tools you can use to speed up your workflow. One of the tools in the suite is a meta description tool. To generate meta descriptions, you must enter your product or business name and description plus the keyword for that <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/posts-vs-pages-in-wordpress/\" title=\"Posts vs. Pages in WordPress — Everything You Need to Know\">page or post</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best factors of Writesonic is that, as a whole, the tool was built for <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-copywriting/\" title=\"10 Best SEO Copywriting Tips for Crafting Content that Converts\">SEO writing</a>. Because of this, you can rest assured that the tool will produce meta descriptions that can help your content rank. This, and other features, make this one of the best meta description tools to consider.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $9/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-meta-description-tools-your-faqs-answered\">Meta Description Tools: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-a-meta-description\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What is a meta description?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>A meta description is a concise summary of the content of a web page. It appears in search engine results and provides a brief overview of what users can expect on the page.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-meta-description-tools\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are meta description tools?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Meta description tools are online resources or software that help website owners and marketers generate, optimize, and analyze meta descriptions for their web pages. These tools often provide suggestions, character count limits, and previews to ensure effective meta descriptions.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-can-meta-description-tools-help-with-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Can meta description tools help with SEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, optimizing meta descriptions is part of on-page SEO, and using meta description tools can help improve the overall SEO performance of a website. A well-optimized meta description can increase click-through rates and enhance the visibility of a page in search engine results.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-best-meta-description-tools-to-boost-your-clickthrough-rate-our-top-pick\">The Best Meta Description Tools to Boost Your Clickthrough Rate: Our Top Pick</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our top pick for the best meta description tool for WordPress is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"Home\">AIOSEO</a>. For one, it’s the easiest to use. All it takes to generate optimized meta descriptions is a single click! Plus, you also get a powerful plugin that can help you improve your visibility on search engines. As a result, you drive more traffic and generate more revenue from your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you find the best SEO audit tool for WordPress. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/wordpress-seo-tips/\" title=\"12 Blogging Tools to Help You Grow Your WordPress Blog\">ultimate WordPress SEO cheat list</a> for beginners or our list of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-blogging-tools/\" title=\"12 Blogging Tools to Help You Grow Your WordPress Blog\">best blogging tools for WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also check out one of our case studies where a content company <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/trends/the-content-authority-seo-case-study/\" title=\"How a Content Services Website Grew Traffic by 300% in 3 Months\">grew their website traffic by 300% in 3months</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.&nbsp;</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-meta-description-tools/\">7 Best Meta Description Tools to Boost Your Clickthrough Rate in 2024</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://aioseo.com/best-meta-description-