(33, 1, '2023-12-01 19:15:06', '2023-12-01 19:15:06', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Poetry Nomad, the poetic gaze of the explorer. If you do not become otherness, you will not understand your personal otherness. If you have no otherness, you are a copy, at least one part of you must be incompatible. And if you don\'t understand it, you won\'t find the unique characteristics that develop you. You follow the crowd.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A part of you must be seriously different from your surroundings, stand out from the background.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>With such thoughts I started the first long road trip. I had been to Europe a few times when I was younger.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://nomadpoetry.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-12-01 19:15:06', '2023-12-01 19:15:06', '', 2, 'https://nomadpoetry.com/?p=33', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
